title: Silicon Valley Season 1
description:
Season One of Silicon Valley on HBO.

All are 720p HDTV rips.  

No one group managed to release every episode of the season, so these rips are not all from the same group.
Episodes 2 and 6 are from 2hd
Episode 7 is from Dimension
All others are Killers

All files are their respective release groups' original, unchanged h264 video and AC3 audio streams, but have been repackaged from mkv to mp4 containers for compatibility with certain home media players.
